critter.name: Goldfish
critter.desc: Goldfish are so cute and delicate... but do you know how big they can get? Why, they can grow up to... a foot in length! Well, sometimes. The size of the tank they're kept in tends to restrict their growth. And just how big will this goldfish get in our large museum tank? I look forward to finding out!
critter.quote: I caught a goldfish! It's worth its weight in fish!
